senior leader deng xiaoping crushed it as he did the 
prodemocracy protests in early june 
yangs magazine coeditor xu wenli is still at prison no 1 in 
his fourth year of solitary confinement song said solitude was 
beneficial to xus individual reform 
he recognizes some of his problems but im afraid there must 
still be a process of reform song said 
