pay fare boosts with prices for all transportation for visitors set 
at 70 percent above what chinese passengers pay according to the 
announcement that is the same price ratio used under the old system 
inflation is running at a rate of 25 percent down from a high of 
36 percent last year but still above acceptable levels for chinas 
communist economy 
